  *Yes! This is the complete tab. for 2x4 - The following is some*  
  *explanation of symbols and the order of riffs, solos and fills.*  
  *~ indicates slide*  
  */ indicates bend up*  
  *^ indicates bend up and release*  
  *\ indicates slide down*  
  *H indicates hammer-on*  
  *P indicates pull-off*  
  *S stands for solo*  
  *R stands for riff*  
  *F stands for fill*  
  
